trans-unit.source: Iterates over all descendant nodes according to the <xref href="System.Xml.XPath"></xref> descendant axis rules.
trans-unit.target: Itererar över alla underordnade noder enligt den <xref href="System.Xml.XPath"> </xref> underordnade axel regler.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator"></xref> that identifies the node from which you start traversing descendants.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator"></xref>som identifierar den nod där du startar passerar underordnade.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter"></xref> class, which enables you to filter nodes based on the name.
trans-unit.target: En instans av den <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter"> </xref> -klassen, som gör att du kan filtrera noder baserat på namn.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Boolean> that indicates whether the current node is returned as part of the iteration or filtered out.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Boolean>värde som anger om den aktuella noden returneras som en del av upprepning eller filtreras ut.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: Tillstånd för Navigatören ändringar endast om den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.MoveNext%2A>metoden returnerade `true`.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator on the next descendant node.
trans-unit.target: Placerar iterator på nästa underordnade nod.

trans-unit.source: If the next descendant node exists, the MoveNext method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.Current%2A> property to the current result navigator; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Om det finns underordnade textnoden metoden MoveNext anger den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.Current%2A>egenskapen till den aktuella resultatet Navigatören; annars den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.Current%2A>egenskapen förblir oförändrad.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DescendantIterator.Current%2A>
